1408.name: Legislature
1408.description: Percentage of respondents who answered that either “Most” or “All” of the elected representatives / legislatures are corrupt.

source.name: Transparency International - GCB (2017)
source.additionalInfo: The Global Corruption Barometer surveys the experiences of everyday people confronting corruption around the world. Data for the most recent report (2017) was collected by either face to face or telephone interviews with adults living in 119 countries around the world. The fieldwork was conducted between March 2014 and January 2017.
